{"tid":648937,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"調查指持雙程證人士缺乏支援","createTime":"2018-05-01T07:02:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T07:42:18.000Z","uid":121420,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"79cc4861c224132a31dc55c0a13a602fea1c0446","tid":648937,"uid":121420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:02:54.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】社區組織協會調查發現，本港對內地來港照顧家人的雙程證人士支援不足。<br />\n<br />\n社區組織協會於去年7月至12月，以問卷訪問逾百名從內地來港照顧家人的持雙程證內地女子，當中包括雙非兒童家長及丈夫已去世或離婚的「分隔單親」。<br />\n<br />\n超過八成人表示面對家庭經濟困難，主要因為沒有身份證而不能工作，約七成半人亦無法受惠社會福利署的服務支援。<br />\n<br />\n社協批評社署未有提供針對性的融合和支援服務，促請當局制訂清晰和全面的新移民政策。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=304265&amp;refer=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D304265%26refer%3Dshare&d=hUgXkzpu5NMhDT%2FrcyqztnadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=fab24073\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D304265%26refer%3Dshare&h=7c2bed8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=304265&amp;refer=share</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22a7ca16eecdcd7acb63e660dffbc832ed5623f8","tid":648937,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:07:26.000Z","msg":"支持雙程證人士盡快落地獄"},{"pid":"e09e37c95438ce0e39c56e8fa1a8137ac840422e","tid":648937,"uid":111573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:13:18.000Z","msg":"家庭困難咪撚落嚟啦屌你老母。"},{"pid":"80d87718a7f5ceed434c5770c4ed9a51bbb7a59f","tid":648937,"uid":135767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T07:42:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}